Description:
   Choke Hold seizes the victim's throat, cutting off blood flow to the
   brain. Deals damage (1d(Pugilist level/4 + 1)) and applies AFF_SLEEP,
   temporarily incapacitating the target for 2 rounds. The incapacitated
   target cannot act, fight back, or flee during this window. A powerful
   control skill at high levels, but the brief duration requires follow-up
   strikes to capitalize on the opening.
